newsitem.title: MALAYSIA: Malaysia July palm oil exports 710,836 -SGS.
newsitem.headline: Malaysia July palm oil exports 710,836 -SGS.

text.p: Cargo surveyor Societe Generale de Surveillance (SGS) Malaysia Sdn Bhd on Thursday it said it estimated Malaysia's palm oil exports for July at 710,836 tonnes against 611,368 tonnes for June.
It said the exports comprised 209,456 tonnes of RBD palm oil, 288,313 tonnes of RBD palm olein and 88,245 tonnes of RBD palm stearin. The other products totalled 124,822 tonnes.
